Products.Title: The Letterbox Mixed Alstroemeria
Products.ShortDescription: this beautiful selection of mixed colours alstroemeria is sent in a special sized letterbox!
Products.Description:
This beautiful selection of mixed colours alstroemeria is sure to brighten anyone's day! The flowers are carefully placed by hand in a specially designed box, and will be delivered in bud, straight through the letterbox, so no need to worry if your recipient is in! 

 
Bouquet Details:
• 5 x Pink Alstroemeria
• 4 x Purple Alstroemeria
• 5 x White Alstroemeria
• Wrapped in frosted cellophane
• Stem length: Approx. 46cm  


Please note the vase is not included.

Our flowers may arrive unopened but the buds will come into bloom within a day or two.

Please note, large cards are too big to fit in our letterbox flowers boxes! If you order this bouquet with a large card it will be sent separately via 1st class post.

Box size 62.2cm x 18.3 cm x 3.7 cm; designed to fit through most standard UK letterboxes. 


In the rare event that a substitution is necessary through flower supply difficulties, we may substitute with flowers of similar or superior style, quality and value.

Our Commitment to Quality:

From blossom to bouquet, every step of your flowers’ journey is handled with care to ensure long-lasting, beautiful blooms. That means:

  • Five days of freshness guaranteed or we’ll replace your flowers
  • Each bouquet is hand-tied by our florists
  • Flowers arrive ‘in bud’ to preserve freshness
  • Guard petals protect roses in transit
  • Bouquets come in our signature Nourishing Wrap to keep them happy while travelling
  • Next day delivery with full SMS tracking and a two hour delivery window
